modName: Thalmor Justiciars Headquarters Actually are Thalmor
summary: Revamps the Thalmor Headquarters in SOlitude so that it actually is worthy of the Thalmor slightly
descriptionHtml:
This removes the Imperial banners seen in the Headquarters and places Thalmor banners in the interior and exterior of the building.

This also adds Thalmor NPCs:

- Thalmor Commander
- 2 male Thalmor guards
- 2 Female Thalmor Guards

This was really my addition to the \"Aldmeri Strengthened\" Mod which enables you to offically join the Thalmor located here:

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32828 -  by linger2717

I hope this is worthy of your fantastic mod, linger2717! This is partially for you also!

*dark elven gear seen in images is a revamp of Thalmor soldiers by using Dark Elven Thalmor-Style Equipment - Standalone
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33223
author: Beth
